Class X2Scale

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.oliviercailloux.xmcda_2_2_1_jaxb.X2Scale

  • public class X2Scale
extends Object
    Description of a scale. Choice between 3 types of scales: nominal, qualitative and quantitative.

    Java class for scale complex type.

   <complexContent>
     <restriction base="{http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema}anyType">

         <element name="valuationType" type="{http://www.decision-deck.org/2012/XMCDA-2.2.1}valuationType" minOccurs="0"/>
         <choice>
           <element name="nominal" type="{http://www.decision-deck.org/2012/XMCDA-2.2.1}nominal"/>
